title: ORDER BY column alias
sql:
select employee_id, 
       floor ( 
         months_between ( sysdate, hire_date ) / 12 
       ) as years_employed
from   hr.employees
order  by years_employed desc
fetch  first 3 rows only

EMPLOYEE_ID YEARS_EMPLOYED
----------- --------------
        102             21
        109             19
        108             19
